lead_paragraph: Houston Rockets forward Corey Brewer had a season-high 24 points and made two three-pointers in the final two minutes to lead his team to a 111-105 victory over the Phoenix Suns at Talking Stick Resort Arena on Thursday.

headline.print_headline: Brewer Lights Touchpaper to Fire Rockets Over Suns
